General information
===================

Libvoikko is a library for Finnish natural language processing. The core
is written in Rust (edition 2024, MSRV 1.86). The VFST backend provides
morphology-based analysis for Finnish.

Libvoikko provides spell checking, hyphenation, grammar checking,
morphological analysis, tokenization, and sentence splitting.


License
=======

The core library is available under MPL 1.1 / GPL 2+ / LGPL 2.1+ tri-license.

 Backend        License
----------------------------------------------------------------
 VFST           MPL 1.1 / GPL 2+ / LGPL 2.1+


Features
========

 - Spell checking using compound word and derivation rule system.
 - Spelling suggestions tuned for common typing errors and OCR correction.
 - Hyphenation with compound-aware splitting based on morphological analysis.
 - Grammar checking and context-sensitive spell checking using paragraph
   based API.
 - String tokenizer and sentence splitter.
 - Morphological analyzer with full inflection details.
 - Available through JS/TS (WASM), Python, Java, C#, Common Lisp, and C APIs.

Documentation for the C API is in rust/crates/voikko-ffi/include/voikko.h.


Directory structure
===================

 rust/          Rust workspace (6 crates, 637 tests)
   crates/
     voikko-core/   Shared types and enums (68 tests)
     voikko-fst/    VFST finite state transducer engine (71 tests)
     voikko-fi/     Finnish language module (494 tests, 10 ignored)
     voikko-wasm/   WebAssembly bindings via wasm-bindgen (189KB, 4 tests)
     voikko-ffi/    C FFI shared library (420KB, 30+ functions)
     voikko-cli/    8 command-line tools

 js/            npm package @yongsk0066/voikko (37 vitest)
 python/        Python ctypes bindings
 java/          Java JNA bindings
 cs/            C# P/Invoke bindings
 cl/            Common Lisp CFFI bindings
 legacy/        Original C++ source (preserved for reference)
 doc/           API documentation
 data/          Grammar help XML (gchelp.xml)


Build (Rust)
============

  cd rust
  cargo fmt --all --check
  cargo test --all-features      # 637 tests
  cargo clippy --all-features -- -D warnings
  cargo audit

WASM build:

  cd rust
  cargo build --target wasm32-unknown-unknown --release -p voikko-wasm
  wasm-bindgen target/wasm32-unknown-unknown/release/voikko_wasm.wasm \
    --out-dir ../js/wasm --target web --typescript
  wasm-opt ../js/wasm/voikko_wasm_bg.wasm -Oz --enable-bulk-memory \
    -o ../js/wasm/voikko_wasm_bg.wasm

FFI shared library:

  cd rust
  cargo build --release -p voikko-ffi
  # produces target/release/libvoikko_ffi.{dylib,so,dll}

JS/TS package:

  cd js
  pnpm install && pnpm build     # dist/index.mjs (14KB)
  pnpm test                      # 37 vitest


Dictionary files
================

For dictionary format 5 (Finnish VFST backend):

 Valid VFST dictionaries can be built from voikko-fi version 2.0 or later.
 The dictionary path should contain: {path}/5/mor-standard/{files}

 Required files:
   - mor.vfst      (morphological transducer, ~3.8MB)
   - autocorr.vfst (autocorrect transducer, ~11KB)
   - index.txt     (dictionary metadata)


